Nie je to chyba.

112
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:56,800
Toto je stalker!

113
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:59,400
Nespravil nič zlé.

114
00:05:59,400 --> 00:06:01,710
Možno je to milý človek

115
00:06:01,710 --> 00:06:04,810
