217
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:48,090
Pri vašom stave by sme to 
mali spraviť čo najskôr.

218
00:10:48,090 --> 00:10:49,430
Nespravím to.

219
00:10:50,400 --> 00:10:52,630
- Myslíte operáciu?
- Áno.

220
00:10:53,300 --> 00:10:54,930
Nechcem to.

221
00:10:55,830 --> 00:10:57,100
prepáčte.

222
00:10:58,200 --> 00:10:59,240
Prečo nie?

223
