234
00:11:45,280 --> 00:11:46,850
Nie, nie.

235
00:11:46,850 --> 00:11:48,350
To z tohto.

236
00:11:49,420 --> 00:11:50,250
Čo?

237
00:11:55,560 --> 00:11:58,360
Prepáčte, že som nebola viac upravená.

238
00:11:59,430 --> 00:12:03,000
Keď som to zbadala, chcela som to napraviť.

239
00:12:04,400 --> 00:12:06,400
Je to choroba z povolania.

240
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:09,710
Pani Tsuruoka, vy ste kaderníčka, však?

